    • Field Detail

      • VERSION

        public String VERSION
        software VERSION. Defined in src/resources/makelangelo.properties and uses Maven's resource filtering to update the VERSION based upon VERSION defined in POM.xml. In this way we only define the VERSION once and prevent violating DRY.
